reviews.text: Old shopping arcade with a necessities that u need.
Only been there for a meal in a budget canteen. Very down to earth canteen for quick meal nothing fancy. Noisy and greasy environment but cheap.
Though usually crowded, but it is one of the few remaining old fashion shopping centers from the 80's with plenty of goods and food.
It is okay
Fascinating old-style shopping centre that offers plenty of much more reasonably priced alternatives to the neighbouring Metroplaza.  Sam Gor and Cafe de Coral are firm favourites.

result.name: 葵涌中心商場

reviews.text: 好殘舊，沒有空調，只有茶餐廳，藥房。二樓全是地產，沒有什麼好值得遊覽！
不討厭，呢處並不止於適合附近住戶
尚有特色小舖，大量入舖街頭小食！
商埸设施比较老舊，一楼多為補習社，地下食肆推荐上海麵小舘，越南牛肉汤麵同B420西式餐厅（注意以上三間星期天全部不营业）
舊式商場！雖然地方比較暗！但有各式各樣嘅鋪頭，買嘢應該好方便！最多嘅舖頭係賣衫同賣食物！有間中旅社！最頂層有超多食物舖頭，其他層數都頗多！如果搵食，去呢個商場都唔錯！
